casebody.head_matter:
In Re Joseph C. GARCIA, petitioner.
No. 18-6890 (18A570).
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 4, 2018.
Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of habeas corpus denied.
